title: Women of iHeartCountry with Amy Brown: Tenille Arts
itunes:title: Women of iHeartCountry with Amy Brown: Tenille Arts
description:
A special edition of a Women of iHeartCountry interview and performance. Amy welcomes Tenille Arts!

Amy and Tenille talked about her new single “Back Then Right Now”, writing her new album over ZOOM, fashion, and what it was like landing her first No.1 this year. 

She also performs her No. 1 song “Somebody Like That”. And be sure to check out Women of iHeartCountry on your local iHeartCountry station every weekend hosted by Amy!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
